"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-world-1928939-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-crticism\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The officialOlympicsaccount appears to have removed the Paris 2024 opening ceremony footage from its YouTube page after the event received widespread criticism.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 68, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999948161076, \"rank\": 5.183995544351544e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of social media users posted screenshots from their devices showing the message 'this video is not available' when trying to watch the coverage back.\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics and Paris 2024 have not issued a statement to explain why the video is not available.\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 341, \"end\": 351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999948161076, \"rank\": 5.183995544351544e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony raised eyebrows with its unconventional style.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It involved models, dancers, fashion icons and drag queens as well as a range of artistic themes.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A scene recreating Leonardo Da Vinci's 'The Last Supper'with drag queens and other performers was among the moments that sparked the biggest reaction.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.379959232672529e-14, \"text\": \"Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.459087861654622e-21, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Olympics row escalates as sponsor pulls out over 'blasphemous' opening ceremony    Tesla and X bossElon Muskwas among the high-profile voices to condemn the ceremony.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"Christianity has become toothless.\\\"\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another moment in the show that caught the eye was a giant platter of fake fruits and other foods with a smurf-looking person sitting on top of them.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The man was dressed as the Greek God of wine, festivity and theatre, Dionysus.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9459203895875169, \"rank\": 0.050930106317451485, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.8466664751388034e-13, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \